<s docid="SJMN91-06311092" num="16" wdcount="34"> His death 
prompted immediate concern in British financial circles 
about the future of his debt-laden empire and in New York 
about the future of the Daily News, one of the nation's 
largest metropolitan papers.</s>

<s docid="FT922-2972" num="8" wdcount="34"> Yet although some 
banks became alarmed at the implications for the financial 
