with each other or with authorities such as the Bank of 
England.</s>

<s docid="SJMN91-06346032" num="24" wdcount="25"> Kevin Maxwell 
has been linked to transactions of a pension fund 
management firm at the center of the controversy over the 
missing money, investigators say.</s>

<s docid="SJMN91-06346032" num="25" wdcount="33"> He and brother 
Ian are under court order to disclose by next week what 
they know about the affairs of Bishopsgate Investment 
Management Ltd., one of about 40 companies controlled by 
their father.</s>

<s docid="FT942-12054" num="6" wdcount="37"> Two writs have been 
